
Enter the src directory

Linux : To compile the code run the command compile.sh
Windows : To compile the code run the command compile.bat

To compile the code run the command compile.bat

To run the application:

Initiate the peers using the folwing command

java communication/Peer <protocol_version> <peer_id> <service_access_point> 224.0.0.0:8000 224.0.0.0:8001 224.0.0.0:8002

protocol_version: 1.0 or 1.1

peer_id: an integer

service_access_point: remote object name

Start testApp using the command:

java communication/TestApp <peer_ap> <operation> <opnd_1> <opnd_2>

example: java communication/TestApp Test1 BACKUP file.txt 1
